    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Authentic Enough</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Bruce Bowdon letter on Karim Butler's August 27 letter on blues music notes B B King has made Susan Tedeschi his heir apparent (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In response to Karim Butler's letter, I note that Susan Tedeschi has spent the entire summer on B. B. King's Blues Tour. During a recent stop in Cincinnati, both Mr. King and Buddy Guy invited her on stage to play with them. If Ms. Tedeschi is authentic enough for the king of the blues and his heir apparent, she's good enough for me.</p>
        <p>BRUCE BOWDON  Cincinnati</p>
      </block>
